extends layout

block content
    #main-content.container
        #featured-container.row
            .featured-slider
                ul
                    each feature in features
                        li
                            .feature(style="background-image: url('#{feature['feature'].image}')" data-id="#{feature['film'].id}")
                                .feature-callout
                                    .feature-title= feature['film'].title
                                    .feature-year (#{feature['film'].year})
                                    .feature-director-container.flex-row.flex-baseline
                                        .feature-by by
                                        .feature-director= feature['film'].director
                                    .feature-studio= feature['film'].studio

        each genre in genrelist
            #genre-container.row
                .heading-bar.flex-row.flex-centered
                    .heading-title=genre
                .heading-diagonal
                .movie-scroll
                    #ca-container.ca-container
                        .ca-wrapper
                            each film in genres[genre]
                                .ca-item(style="background-image: url('#{film.poster}'); background-size: cover;").ca-item-1
                                    .ca-item-main
                                        a.ca-more(href='#') more...
                                    .ca-content-wrapper
                                        .ca-content
                                            h6 Test
                                            a.ca-close(href='#') close
                                            .ca-content-text
                                                p
                                                    | I am so happy, my dear friend, so absorbed in the exquisite sense of mere tranquil existence, that I neglect my talents. I should be incapable of drawing a single stroke at the present moment; and yet I feel that I never was a greater artist than now.
                                                p
                                                    | When, while the lovely valley teems with vapour around me, and the meridian sun strikes the upper surface of the impenetrable foliage of my trees, and but a few stray gleams steal into the inner sanctuary, I throw myself down among the tall grass by the trickling stream;
                                                p
                                                    | She packed her seven versalia, put her initial into the belt and made herself on the way.
                                            ul
                                                li
                                                    a(href='#') Read more
                                                li
                                                    a(href='#') Share this
                                                li
                                                    a(href='#') Become a member
                                                li
                                                    a(href='#') Donate

        include footer
    script(src="/javascripts/index.js")